    "body" : "<p>I stumbled across this question by accident and felt it needed a Java 8 update using streams:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static List&lt;Field&gt; getStatics(Class&lt;?&gt; clazz) {\n    List&lt;Field&gt; result;\n\n    result = Arrays.stream(clazz.getDeclaredFields())\n            // filter out the non-static fields\n            .filter(f -&gt; Modifier.isStatic(f.getModifiers()))\n            // collect to list\n            .collect(toList());\n\n    return result;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Obviously, that sample is a bit embelished for readability. In actually, you would likely write it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static List&lt;Field&gt; getStatics(Class&lt;?&gt; clazz) {\n    return Arrays.stream(clazz.getDeclaredFields()).filter(f -&gt;\n        Modifier.isStatic(f.getModifiers())).collect(toList());\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
